metadata.name: Whispering Witch - Poppy #1/50
metadata.description:
The Whispering Witches {of Poland}, are a clandestine faction of haunting women who heal in whispers. 
This particular piece embodies my own vision of one of these witches centered around Poland's national flower; the poppy. They have been cultivated for centuries and used medicinally, in the kitchen and magickally. The poppy is feminine and resonates to the energy of the moon.
